#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game type: Arcade, Strategy"
msgstr "Tip igre: Arkadno, Strategija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of players: One"
msgstr "Broj igrača: Jedan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kgoldrunner; is an action game where the hero runs through a maze and "
"dodges enemies. You must guide the hero with the mouse or keyboard and "
"collect all the gold nuggets, then you can climb up into the next level. "
"Your enemies are also after the gold. Worse still, they are after you! They "
"will kill you if they catch you!"
msgstr ""
"&kgoldrunner; je akciona igrica gdje heroj prolazi kroz labirint "
"izbjegavajući neprijatelje. Morate voditi vašeg heroja pomoću miša ili "
"tastature i pokupiti grumene zlata, tek tada možete preći na sledeći nivo. "
"Vaši neprijatelji također žele zlato, Ali ono što je možda i gore jeste da "
"žele i vas ! Ako vas uhvate gotovi ste !"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The problem is you have no weapon to kill <emphasis>them</emphasis>. All you "
"can do is run away, dig holes in the floor to trap them or lure them into "
"some area where they cannot hurt you. After a short time a trapped enemy "
"climbs out of his hole, but if it closes before that, he will die and "
"reappear somewhere else."
msgstr ""
"Problem je što ste nemate oružje da ubijete <emphasis>njih</emphasis>. "
"Jedino sto možete je bježati, kopati zamke ili ih namamiti takmo gdje vam ne "
"mogu nauditi. Poslije nekog vremena neprijatelji se mogu osloboditi iz "
"zamke, ali ako se zamka zatvori prije toga, onda će umrijeti i pojaviti se "
"negdje drugo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have never played before, try the <quote>Tutorial</quote> game, which "
"teaches you the rules and basic skills. Then try the <quote>Initiation</"
"quote> game. Experts might enjoy the <quote>Challenge</quote>, "
"<quote>Vengeance of Peter W</quote>, <quote>Count</quote> or <quote>Curse of "
"the Mummy</quote> games, but the <quote>Initiation</quote> game has 100 "
"levels and some are very difficult. It is a good game for achieving a High "
"Score."
msgstr ""
"If you have never played before, try the <quote>Tutorial</quote> game, which "
"teaches you the rules and basic skills. Poslije probajte <quote>Inicijaciju</"
"quote> . Iskusniji mogu uživati u  <quote>Izazovu</quote>, <quote>Osveti  "
"Petera W</quote>, <quote>Brojanju</quote> ili <quote>Kletvi Mumije</quote> , "
"ali  <quote>Inicijacia</quote> ima 100 različitih nivoa od kojih si neki "
"jako teši. Inicijacija je odlična za postizanje Najboljeg Rezultata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All those games use Traditional rules, which are similar to those used on "
"early home-computers, such as the Apple II or Commodore 64. The "
"<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> and <quote>State of Terror</quote> games use "
"&kgoldrunner; rules, in which the enemies run faster and have a more "
"aggressive search strategy than in Traditional rules. See <link linkend="
"\"choice-of-rules\">Choice of Rules</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Sve ove igrice koriste stara pravila, koja su slična onima na prvim kućnim "
"računarima kao što su Apple II ili Commodore 64.<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> "
"i<quote>Zemlja Terora</quote>  igre koriste &kgoldrunner; pravila gdje "
"neprijatelji trče brže i imaju agresivniju strategiju za razliku od starih "
"pravila. Vidi <link linkend=\"choice-of-rules\">Izbor Pravila</link>  za "
"detalje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you move to more advanced levels, you will find that &kgoldrunner; "
"combines action, strategy, tactics and puzzle solving &mdash; all in one "
"game. Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"Kako napredujete u igrici, shvatit ćete da je &kgoldrunner;  kombinacija "
"akcije,strategije, taktike i mozganja &mdash; sve u jednoj igrici. Sretno !"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Typical Game"
msgstr "Standardna  Igra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a typical game in progress. The hero is at level 4 in the Advanced "
"Tutorial game. The window's lower part shows how many lives he has left and "
"how many points he has scored. It also shows that there is a hint available "
"for this level (as there always is in tutorial games) and that the action is "
"stopped (while taking this snapshot), but can be continued by pressing "
"<keycap>P</keycap> or &Esc;."
msgstr ""
"Ispod vidite standardnu igru. Naš heroj je trenutno na četvrtom nivou "
"Napredne Tutorijalske igre. U donjem dijelu ekrana vidite koliko još života "
"je ostalo i koliki broj poena. Također je prikazano da možete iskoristiti "
"pomoć(kao i u svakoj tutorijalskoj igrici) i da je igrica zaustavljena "
"( ovim prikazom ekrana), ali se može nastaviti ako pritisnete  <keycap>P</"
"keycap> ili &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The hero started at the top left, dug a hole and dropped into a line of "
"false bricks and gold where you can now see him falling. The enemy above him "
"will fall into the hole, then climb out and be trapped up there till the end "
"of the level. He could cause the hero some problems then, because that is "
"where the hidden ladders appear when all the gold is gone. The hero has to "
"use them to get to the next level."
msgstr ""
"Heroj je počeo u gornjem lijevom uglu, iskopao rupu i propao kroz liniju "
"lažnih cigli i zlata. Neprijatelj iznad ce upasti u rupu, zatim se popeti i "
"biti zarobljen gore do kraja nivoa. Ovo može otežati stvari našem heroju jer "
"je to mijesto gdje se nalaze skrivene merdevine i zlato, koje mu je potrebno "
"za sledeći nivo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kgoldrunner; typical game</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kgoldrunner; standardna igra</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kgoldrunner; typical game</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kgoldrunner; standardna igra </phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The enemy on the right is falling and carrying some gold. The third enemy is "
"about to come down a ladder to chase the hero, who will have to dodge both "
"enemies when he reaches the floor. This level also shows diggable bricks and "
"undiggable concrete and has lots of traps (false bricks), which look just "
"like ordinary bricks."
msgstr ""
"Neprijatelj sa desne strane pada i nosi zlato. Treći neprijatelj silazi sa "
"merdevina da bi zaganjao našeg heroja, koji će morati izbjećo oba "
"neprijatelja prije nego dođe do poda.Ovaj nivo također sadrzi  dosta cigli "
"kroz koje se može kopati ali također i dosta lažnih cigli koje su zamke "
"napravljene da izgledaju kao obične cigle i beton kroz koji se ne može "
"kopati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "How To Play"
msgstr "Kako Igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting the Game"
msgstr "Početak Igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kgoldrunner; begins by showing you a recorded demonstration of play. You "
#| "can terminate this by clicking on the playing area with the mouse, "
#| "pressing the spacebar or selecting a menu item or shortcut (such as "
#| "<menuchoice> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Game...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>). You can skip this demonstration in future by "
#| "using menu item <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo "
#| "At Start</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. You can also see it again at any "
#| "time by using menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Move</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"&kgoldrunner; begins by showing you a recorded demonstration of play. You "
"can terminate this by clicking on the playing area with the mouse, pressing "
"the &Space; bar or selecting a menu item or shortcut (such as <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Game…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>). You can "
"skip this demonstration in future by using menu item <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo At Start</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. You can also see it again at any time by using menu item "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kgoldrunner; počinje prikazivanjem isječka igrice. Možete prekinuti klikom "
"miša, pritiskom na spacebar ili  izborom opcije sa menija ili kratice (kao "
"što su  <menuchoice> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova Igra...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>). Ubuduće možete prekinuti isječak krosteći na "
"meniju <menuchoice> <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Isječak pri "
"pokretanju</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Također možete vidjeti isječak bilo "
"kada koristeći <menuchoice><guimenu>Pokreni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Isječak</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you skipped the demo or used the mouse or spacebar to end it, a quick-"
#| "start popup dialog box shows you the names, number and a preview of the "
#| "last game and level you loaded or, if you have not played before, the "
#| "same information for Tutorial level 1."
msgid ""
"If you skipped the demo or used the mouse or &Space; bar to end it, a quick-"
"start popup dialog shows you the names, number and a preview of the last "
"game and level you loaded or, if you have not played before, the same "
"information for Tutorial level 1."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste preskočili isječak ili ga prekinuli, iskakajući interfejs će vam "
"prikazati ime, broj i prikaz zadnje igrice koju ste pokrenuli, u slučaju da "
"ranije nista igrali prikazat ce se informacije za nivo jedan Tutorijala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click on the <guibutton>PLAY</guibutton> button to begin playing "
#| "immediately. Otherwise you can click on the <guibutton>Quit</guibutton> "
#| "button, the <guibutton>New Game</guibutton> button or the <guibutton>Use "
#| "Menu</guibutton> button. The first will close &kgoldrunner;, if you do "
#| "not wish to play, the second will show you a <link linkend=\"level-"
#| "selection-dialog\">Level Selection</link> dialog, where you can choose a "
#| "different game and level and the last will terminate the dialog, leaving "
#| "you free to use the &kgoldrunner; menus."
msgid ""
"Click on the <guibutton>PLAY</guibutton> button to begin playing "
"immediately. Otherwise you can click on the <guibutton>Quit</guibutton> "
"button, the <guibutton>New Game…</guibutton> button or the <guibutton>Use "
"Menu</guibutton> button. The first will close &kgoldrunner;, if you do not "
"wish to play, the second will show you a <link linkend=\"select-game-dialog"
"\">Select Game</link> dialog, where you can choose a different game and "
"level and the last will terminate the dialog, leaving you free to use the "
"&kgoldrunner; menus."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite  na <guibutton>Igraj</guibutton> da odmah počnete igrati. Ili "
"kliknite na <guibutton>Prekid </guibutton> ,<guibutton>Nova Igra</guibutton> "
"ili <guibutton>Koristi Meni</guibutton>. Prvo će zatvoriti &kgoldrunner;, "
"ako ne želite nastaviti prikazat će se <link linkend=\"level-selection-dialog"
"\">Izbor Nivoa</link>  dijalog, gdje možete izabrati drugu igricu ili novo i "
"posljednje će zatvoriti dijalog, ostavljajući vama da slobodno koristite "
"&kgoldrunner; menije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you have chosen to play a game and level, it will then appear and the "
#| "pointer will be over the hero. In a tutorial game, an explanatory message "
#| "appears before each level begins. You start play by moving the pointer, "
#| "clicking the mouse or pressing any key that can control the hero (&eg; "
#| "<keycap>Space</keycap>), but avoid using <keycap>Q</keycap>, <keycap>S</"
#| "keycap>, <keycap>P</keycap> or &Esc; at this stage. You start each level "
#| "in the same way."
msgid ""
"If you have chosen to play a game and level, it will then appear and the "
"pointer will be over the hero. In a tutorial game, an explanatory message "
"appears before each level begins. You start play by moving the pointer, "
"clicking the mouse or pressing any key that can control the hero (&eg; "
"&Space;), but avoid using <keycap>Q</keycap>, <keycap>S</keycap>, <keycap>P</"
"keycap> or &Esc; at this stage. You start each level in the same way."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste izabrali da igrajte  igru i nivoe , ona će se pojaviti i pokazivat "
"će iznad heroja. U igri tutorial , pojavljuje objašnjenja poruka prije "
"početka svakog nivoa . Počinjete igru pomicanjem pokazivača , klikom miša "
"ili pritiskom na bilo koju tipku koja može  kontrolirati heroja (&eg; "
"<keycap>Space</keycap>), ali izbjegavajte koristiti <keycap>Q</keycap>, "
"<keycap>S</keycap>, <keycap>P</keycap> ili &Esc;u ovoj fazi . Počinjete "
"svaki nivo na isti način ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have five lives at the start and gain a bonus life for each level "
"completed."
msgstr "Imate pet života na početku plus po jedan život za svaki završen nivo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving Around"
msgstr "Kretanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default you control the hero with the mouse, but you can also control him "
"with the keyboard (<link linkend=\"keyboard-control\">see below</link>) or, "
"on a laptop, by using a mix of the keyboard for digging and the touchpad or "
"other pointer device to guide the hero."
msgstr ""
"Unaprijed je određeno da kontrolišete heroja mišem, ali ga možete "
"kontrolisati i tastatruom (<link linkend=\"keyboard-control\">vidi ispod</"
"link>) ili ako koristite laptom mješavinom tastature, za kopanje, i tačpeda "
"ili miša za kretanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The hero moves towards wherever you place the pointer. He cannot move as "
"fast as you can move the pointer, but he will try hard to catch up. If the "
"pointer is above or below his level, he will always go up or down when there "
"is a ladder available or a place to fall into. Otherwise he will move "
"horizontally until he is below the pointer, above it or right at it. You can "
"make him follow simple paths (like &mdash; | L or U), but be careful not to "
"get too many twists and turns ahead of him."
msgstr ""
"Heroj se kreće prema mijestu gdje pokažete. Ne može se kretati istom brzinom "
"kojom vi pokazujete pokazivačem, ali će se potruditi da sustigne sto prije. "
"Ako je pokazivač nivo iznad ili ispod ići će ispod ili iznad, ukoliko imaju "
"merdevine ili rupa kroz koji može proći, u protivnom kretati će se "
"horizontalno dok ne bude iznad ili ispod pokazivača. Možete ga navoditi "
"jednostavnim putevima (kao &mdash; | L ili U), samo pazite da pravite "
"previše naglih skretanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move left or right over bricks, concrete, ladders or bars and up or "
"down over ladders. If you are on an empty square or a gold nugget and there "
"is no brick, concrete, ladder or bar to hold you up, gravity takes over and "
"you fall. You can also fall by moving down from a bar or the bottom of a "
"ladder, so keep the pointer up there if you want to hold on."
msgstr ""
"Možete se kretati lijevo ili desno  preko cigli, betona, merdevina ili "
"prečki, i gore dolje preko merdevina. Ako ste na praznom polju ili grumenu "
"zlata i nema cigli,betona merdevina ili prečke da vas drži, onda će "
"gravitacija uraditi svoje. Također možete pasti sa prečke i merdevina ako ne "
"držite pokazivač prema gore."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Control"
msgstr "Kontrole Tastature"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you prefer, you can use the keyboard to control the hero. The default "
#| "keys are the arrow keys and <keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, "
#| "<keycap>K</keycap> and <keycap>L</keycap> (in honor of the original Apple "
#| "II game), with the keys <keycap>Z</keycap> and <keycap>C</keycap> or "
#| "<keycap>U</keycap> and <keycap>O</keycap> for digging. You can play one-"
#| "handed by using <keycap>U</keycap>, <keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>O</"
#| "keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, <keycap>K</keycap>, <keycap>L</keycap> and "
#| "<keycap>Space</keycap> (on a <quote>QWERTY</quote> keyboard) or two-"
#| "handed by using the arrow keys, <keycap>Space</keycap>, <keycap>Z</"
#| "keycap> and <keycap>C</keycap>. You can also choose other keys, on the "
#| "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu, using the <guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "Shortcuts</guimenuitem> item."
msgid ""
"If you prefer, you can use the keyboard to control the hero. The default "
"keys are the arrow keys and <keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, "
"<keycap>K</keycap> and <keycap>L</keycap> (in honor of the original Apple II "
"game), with the keys <keycap>Z</keycap> and <keycap>C</keycap> or <keycap>U</"
"keycap> and <keycap>O</keycap> for digging. You can play one-handed by using "
"<keycap>U</keycap>, <keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>O</keycap>, <keycap>J</"
"keycap>, <keycap>K</keycap>, <keycap>L</keycap> and &Space; (on a "
"<quote>QWERTY</quote> keyboard) or two-handed by using the arrow keys, "
"&Space;, <keycap>Z</keycap> and <keycap>C</keycap>. You can also choose "
"other keys, on the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite možete koristiti kontrole na tastaturi. Unaprijed postavljene "
"kontrole su strelice i <keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, <keycap>K</"
"keycap> and <keycap>L</keycap> (u čast  Apple II igre), sa tipkom <keycap>Z</"
"keycap> i<keycap>C</keycap> ili <keycap>U</keycap> i <keycap>O</keycap> za "
"kopanje. Možete igrati jednom rukom koristeći<keycap>U</keycap>, <keycap>I</"
"keycap>, <keycap>O</keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, <keycap>K</keycap>, "
"<keycap>L</keycap> and <keycap>Space</keycap> (na<quote>QWERTY</quote> "
"tastaturi) ili sa dvije ruke koristeći, <keycap>Space</keycap>, <keycap>Z</"
"keycap> and <keycap>C</keycap>. Također možete podestiti kontrole na "
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> meniju, koristeći <guimenuitem>Podesi Kratice</"
"guimenuitem> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You enter keyboard mode by pressing one of the keys that can control the "
#| "hero or by selecting <guimenuitem>Keyboard Controls Hero</guimenuitem> on "
#| "the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu."
msgid ""
"You enter keyboard mode by pressing one of the keys that can control the "
"hero or by selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Keyboard Controls Hero</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ulazite i mod tastature pritiskajući jedau od tipki koja kontroliše heroja "
"tako što cje te označiti  <guimenuitem>Kontrole tastature </guimenuitem>na  "
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The movement keys (<keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, <keycap>K</"
#| "keycap>, <keycap>L</keycap> or arrows) start the hero moving up, down, "
#| "left or right. He continues moving in that direction, if he can, until "
#| "you press another movement key or <keycap>Space</keycap> to stop. In "
#| "mouse or laptop mode, he stops automatically when he gets to the pointer."
msgid ""
"The movement keys (<keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, <keycap>K</"
"keycap>, <keycap>L</keycap> or arrows) start the hero moving up, down, left "
"or right. He continues moving in that direction, if he can, until you press "
"another movement key or &Space; to stop. In mouse or laptop mode, he stops "
"automatically when he gets to the pointer."
msgstr ""
"Tipke za kretanje (<keycap>I</keycap>, <keycap>J</keycap>, <keycap>K</"
"keycap>, <keycap>L</keycap> ili strelice) pokreću heroj gore,dole,lijevo ili "
"desno. Nastavlja se kretati u izabranom smijeru dok može, sve dok ne "
"pritisnete drugu tipku ili <keycap>Space</keycap> za zaustavljanje.Ako "
"korisite miš ili laptop, staje automatski kada dođe do pokazivača."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A word of warning: using the keyboard is much harder, in the long run, than "
"using the mouse. Think of the mouse as a joystick."
msgstr ""
"Malo upozorenje: igrati tastaturom je mnogo teže nego koristiti miš. "
"Razmislite da koristite đojstik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taking a Break"
msgstr "Uzmite Pauzu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can stop the game at any time by pressing a Pause key (the default is "
#| "either <keycap>P</keycap> or &Esc;). You can resume by pressing the Pause "
#| "key again. There is also a <guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem> option in the "
#| "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> menu, but the problem is to get the pointer up "
#| "there without moving the hero and getting into trouble."
msgid ""
"You can stop the game at any time by pressing a Pause key (the default is "
"either <keycap>P</keycap> or &Esc;). You can resume by pressing the Pause "
"key again. There is also a <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, but the problem is "
"to get the pointer up there without moving the hero and getting into trouble."
msgstr ""
"Možete zaustaviti igru bilo kada pritiskom na Pauzu(unaprijed određena tipka "
"je <keycap>P</keycap> ili &Esc;). Možete nastaviti ponovnim pritiskom na "
"Pauzu. Također postoji i <guimenuitem>Pauza</guimenuitem> opcija u "
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> meniju, ali problem je kako dovesti pokazivač gore a "
"da se ne ugrozi život heroja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you want to use the &kgoldrunner; menu or do some work in another "
"window, always press a Pause key and stop the game. Otherwise the hero will "
"go on following the pointer and might get into trouble."
msgstr ""
"Kada želite da koristite &kgoldrunner; meni ili želite da koristite neki "
"drugi prozor, uvijek pristisnite Pauzu da prekinete igru. U protivnom heroj "
"će se nastaviti kretati prema pokazivaču."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Winning a Level"
msgstr "Pobijediti Nivo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The object of the game is to collect all the gold, by moving or falling onto "
"it. When there is none left, you must move to the top of the playing area to "
"get to the next level. Often, as you collect the last piece of gold, hidden "
"ladders will appear and you can use them to climb to the top. Sometimes "
"there are no hidden ladders. Also, very rarely, the hidden ladders could be "
"a decoy that leads the wrong way. If the level has no gold, there will be no "
"hidden ladders and you just have to work out how to get to the top of the "
"playing area."
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je pokupiti svo zlato. Kada ga više ne bude, morate se popeti na "
"vrh nivoa da dođete do sledećeg. Često će se skrivene merdevine pokazati "
"kada pokupite zadnje zlato. Ponekad nema skrivenih merdevina. Također, iako "
"veoma rijetko, skrivene merdevine mogu biti varka koja će vas odvesti "
"pogrešnim putem. Ako nivo nema zlata neće biti ni skrivenih merdevina pa je "
"na vama samo da dođete do vrha."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Beware of False Bricks"
msgstr "Pazite se lažnih cigli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"False bricks, otherwise known as fall-through bricks or traps, are the other "
"hidden feature of the game. They look just like ordinary bricks, but if you "
"run over one you fall. This can be bad if there is an enemy or a pit down "
"there, or good if there is some gold."
msgstr ""
"Lažne cigle ili poznate kao propadajuće cigle ili zamke, su jedna od "
"skrivenih opcija igre. Izgledaju isto kao obične cigle,ali ako pređete preko "
"njih, propast će te. Što je loše ako je neprijatelj ispod njih ili dobro ako "
"je zlato ispod njih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enemies"
msgstr "Neprijatelji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enemies move in very much the same way as the hero. The main difference is "
"when they fall into a hole the hero has dug (see <link linkend=\"importance-"
"of-digging\">The Importance of Digging</link> below)."
msgstr ""
"Neprijatelji se kreću isto kao i heroj. Glavna razlika je kada oni propadnu "
"u ruku koju je heroj iskopao(vidi <link linkend=\"importance-of-digging"
"\">Važnost Kopanja</link>ispod)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They will pick up gold either always or at random, depending on the game "
"settings, and will drop gold at random on brick, concrete or the top of a "
"ladder. If an enemy is carrying the last piece of gold, you must get it away "
"from him before you can finish the level."
msgstr ""
"Neprijatelji kupe zlato uvijek ili samo ponekad, zavisno od postavki, i "
"ispuštaju ga na nasumičnu ciglu,beton ili na vrh merdevina. Ako neprijatelj "
"nosi zadnji grumen zlata, morate ga uzeti od njega prije nego završite nivo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an enemy touches you, you die and must start the level again, provided "
"you have some lives left. However, it is possible to walk or stand on an "
"enemy's head and you can ride an enemy down when he is falling. Some "
"advanced levels require such a move."
msgstr ""
"Ako vas neprijatelj dodirne, gubite život i počinjete nivo iz početka, "
"ukoliko to nije bio zadnji život. Ipak moguće je stati na glavu naprijatelja "
"i gurnuti ga prema dole kada pada. Neki od naprednijih nivoa zahtijevaju "
"ovakav potez."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Losing a Level"
msgstr "Gubljenje Nivoa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As explained above, you can lose a level and a life by touching an enemy. "
#| "You can also lose by getting caught in a dug brick when it closes. "
#| "Otherwise you can commit suicide by pressing key <keycap>Q</keycap> or "
#| "using the menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kill "
#| "Hero</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Why would you want to do that? Well, "
#| "sometimes you can get trapped in a place from which you cannot escape. "
#| "You will stay imprisoned for ever unless you commit suicide!"
msgid ""
"As explained above, you can lose a level and a life by touching an enemy. "
"You can also lose by getting caught in a dug brick when it closes. Otherwise "
"you can commit suicide by pressing key <keycap>Q</keycap> or using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kill Hero</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item. Why would you want to do that? Well, sometimes you "
"can get trapped in a place from which you cannot escape. You will stay "
"imprisoned for ever unless you commit suicide!"
msgstr ""
"Kako je objašnjeno iznad, možete izgubiti nivo ili život ako dodirnete "
"neprijatelja. Ili ako budete zarobljeni u rupi kada se zatvori. Ili možete "
"se ubiti ako pritisnete tipku <keycap>Q</keycap> ili koristeći opciju na "
"meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Samoubistvo</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Zašto bi se ubili? Pa, ponekad kada se zaglavite "
"ovo je jedini izlaz."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Importance of Digging"
msgstr "Važnost Kopanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Digging is one of the most powerful tactics you have. To dig a hole in a "
"brick to the left or right, just click the <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> "
"or <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> mouse button, or use one of the digging "
"keys (defaults <keycap>Z</keycap>, <keycap>C</keycap>, <keycap>U</keycap>, "
"<keycap>O</keycap>.)"
msgstr ""
"Kopanje je jedna od najvažnijih taktika. Da iskopate rupu u cigli lijevo ili "
"desno, jednostavno kliknite <mousebutton>Lijevo</mousebutton> "
"ili<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> na mišu, ili tipke na tastaturi za "
"kopanje(ubaprijed određene su <keycap>Z</keycap>, <keycap>C</keycap>, "
"<keycap>U</keycap>, <keycap>O</keycap>.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can dodge an oncoming enemy by digging a hole, waiting for him to fall "
"in and then running quickly over his head. At the same time you can collect "
"any gold he was carrying. Usually you can dig two holes to capture and run "
"over two enemies who are close together, but this rarely works if the "
"enemies are separated or there are more than two of them."
msgstr ""
"Možete izbjegavati neprijatelje kopajući rupe, i čekati da oni u njih upadnu "
"pa pretrčati preko njihovih glava. U isto vrijeme možete pokupiti zlato koje "
"su nosili. često možete iskopati dvije tupe ako su neprijatelji blizu jedan "
"drugog, ali ovo rijetko kad upali ako su odaljeni ili ih ima više od dvojice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can kill enemies by digging enough holes in their path. It usually takes "
"two or more holes to kill one enemy and up to eight or more holes to kill "
"four or five. When enemies die, they reappear immediately, either where they "
"started the level or near the top of the playing area, depending on whether "
"the game follows <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> or <quote>Traditional</quote> "
"rules and settings (see <link linkend=\"choice-of-rules\">Choice of Rules</"
"link>)."
msgstr ""
"Možete ubiti neprijatelje kopajući dovoljno rupa na njihovom putu. Otprilike "
"treba iskopati dvije ili više rupa za svakog ili oko osam ili više da se "
"ubiju četvorica ili petorica. Kada neprijatelju umru, pojavit će se gdje su "
"bili na početku nivoa ili blizu vrha prostora gdje se igra, zavisno kako "
"igra teče <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> ili <quote>Standardno</quote> pravila "
"i postavke (vidi <link linkend=\"choice-of-rules\">Izbor Pravila</link>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, in many levels the gold is not immediately accessible and you must "
"dig to get to it. Some of these digging puzzles are quite complex and you "
"must work out a digging sequence then perform it in limited time before you "
"can complete the level."
msgstr ""
"Konačno, u većini nivoa morat ćete kopati da dođete do zlata. Neke od ovih "
"mozglica gdje kopati su prilično teške tako da morate skontati gdje kopati "
"prije nego vrijeme istekne da bi završili nivo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Rules of Digging"
msgstr "Pravila Kopanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Digging is one of the most powerful tactics you have. To dig a hole in a "
#| "brick to the left or right, just click the <mousebutton>Left</"
#| "mousebutton> or <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> mouse button, or use one "
#| "of the digging keys (defaults <keycap>Z</keycap>, <keycap>C</keycap>, "
#| "<keycap>U</keycap>, <keycap>O</keycap>.)"
msgid ""
"You click the <mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> or <mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> mouse button, to dig a hole to the left or right, or use the "
"<keycap>Z</keycap>, <keycap>C</keycap>, <keycap>U</keycap> or <keycap>O</"
"keycap> keys."
msgstr ""
"Kopanje je jedna od najvažnijih taktika. Da iskopate rupu u cigli lijevo ili "
"desno, jednostavno kliknite <mousebutton>Lijevo</mousebutton> "
"ili<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> na mišu, ili tipke na tastaturi za "
"kopanje(ubaprijed određene su <keycap>Z</keycap>, <keycap>C</keycap>, "
"<keycap>U</keycap>, <keycap>O</keycap>.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only bricks can be dug, not anything else. The hole will appear in the floor "
"on one side or the other (&ie; below and to the left or right of the hero). "
"There must be an empty space or hole above the brick (&ie; no digging under "
"a ladder, bar, gold, brick, concrete or false brick). You can be running, "
"standing or riding down on a falling enemy when you dig. Digging while "
"falling through thin air or false bricks is allowed in some games but not "
"others. See <link linkend=\"dig-while-falling\">Digging while Falling</link> "
"below."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The hero can move in any direction through dug holes, including falling "
"right through a hole to escape an enemy. After a short time, dug holes close "
"up, so you must use them quickly. Plan your digging in advance. There is no "
"time to stop and think while you dig."
msgstr ""
"Heroj se može kretati u svim pravcima kroz rupu uključujući i prema dole da "
"bi izbjegao neprijatelje. Nakon nekog vremena rupe se zatvore, tako da ih "
"morate brzo iskoristiti. Unaprijed razmislite gdje kopati. Nećete imati puno "
"vremena da razmislite u toku igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enemies are always captured if they fall into a dug hole and will always "
"climb UP to get out of it. Their time in the hole is less than the time the "
"hole stays open, so to kill enemies you usually have to dig several holes in "
"quick succession. Enemies always give up gold as they fall into a hole, so "
"you can quickly run onto the enemy's head and grab the gold before he climbs "
"out."
msgstr ""
"Neprijatelji su uvijek zarobljeni ako upadnu u rupu ali će se uvijek i "
"izvući iz nje. Vrijeme koje su u rupu je kraće od onog potrebnog da se rupa "
"zatvori, tako da bi ste ubili neprijatelje morate iskopate nekoliko rupa "
"uzastopno. Neprijatelju uvijek ispuste zlato prije nego upadnu u rupu. Tako "
"da se možete odgurnuti od njihovu glavu i pokupiti zlato prije nego se "
"izvuku iz rupe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enemies will never fall down through a hole from above, but depending on the "
"game rules and <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> (see <link linkend=\"choice-of-"
"rules\">Choice of Rules</link>), they can run horizontally into a dug hole "
"and not be captured and can fall from there or run into another hole or run "
"out of the hole. Several levels that follow <quote>Traditional</quote> rules "
"depend on an enemy being able to run through a hole. Some levels that follow "
"<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> rules depend on an enemy NOT being able to run "
"through a hole."
msgstr ""
"Neprijatelji ne mogu propasti kroz rupu odozgo, ali zavisno od pravila igre "
"i <guimenu>Postavki</guimenu> (vidi <link linkend=\"choice-of-rules\">Izbor "
"Pravila </link>, mogu horizontalno pretrčati rupu da ne budu zaglavljeni ili "
"odatle upasti u drugu rupu. Nekoliko nivoa koji koriste <quote>Standardna</"
"quote> pravila zavise od sposobnosti neprijatelje a trče kroz rupe. A neki "
"koji slijede <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> pravila zavise sposobnosti "
"neprijatelja da NE MOGU trčati kroz rupe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Digging while Falling"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the original game on Apple II and Commodore 64, the hero had to be "
"supported on something solid when digging: a ladder, concrete, a brick, a "
"bar --- or an enemy's head. This rule was overlooked in &kgoldrunner; and "
"one day the author's son discovered that you could dig while falling! He "
"immediately composed a level to exploit this. Other game composers have now "
"done the same. You have to dig while falling in recent games of Championship "
"skill such as <quote>State of Terror</quote>, <quote>Curse of the Mummy</"
"quote> and <quote>Gold Rush</quote>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the other hand, digging while falling makes older games too easy. So, as "
"of December 2015, it is forbidden in the <quote>Tutorial</quote>, "
"<quote>Advanced Tutorial</quote>, <quote>Initiation</quote>, "
"<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> and <quote>Challenge</quote> games. The "
"<quote>Vengeance of Peter W</quote> game allows it in just one level and the "
"new <quote>Beginner's Luck</quote> game, which is aimed at first time "
"players, does not allow it."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Winning and Losing the Game"
msgstr "Pobjeda i Poraz u Igri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You win by completing the last level in the game. You lose when your last "
"life is gone. Either way, if you have achieved one of the ten highest scores "
"for that game, you can record your achievement in the <quote>&kgoldrunner; "
"Hall of Fame</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Pobjeđujete kada završite poslednji nivo. Gubite kada izgubite poslednji "
"život. Bilo kako bilo, ako uspijete postići jedan od deset rekorda, možete "
"zabilježiti vaš uspijeh u <quote>&kgoldrunner; Domu Slavnih</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recordings, Replays and Solutions"
msgstr "Snimci, Ponavno gledanje i Rješenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "All levels in games are recorded as you play, so you can replay any level "
#| "you have previously played. Also, some levels have recorded solutions, "
#| "which may help you work out how to win them. Just use the <guimenu>Move</"
#| "guimenu> menu and items <guimenuitem>Show A Solution</guimenuitem>, "
#| "<guimenuitem>Instant Replay</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Replay Last "
#| "Level</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Replay Any Level</guimenuitem>. The "
#| "solutions and replays can be interrupted at any time by clicking with the "
#| "mouse on the playing area, pressing the spacebar or selecting a menu item "
#| "or shortcut (such as <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New "
#| "Game...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgid ""
"All levels in games are recorded as you play, so you can replay any level "
"you have previously played. Also, some levels have recorded solutions, which "
"may help you work out how to win them. Just use the <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"menu and the <guimenuitem>Show a Solution</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Instant Replay</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Replay Last Level</"
"guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Replay Any Level</guimenuitem> options. The "
"solutions and replays can be interrupted at any time by clicking with the "
"mouse on the playing area, pressing the &Space; bar or selecting a menu item "
"or shortcut (such as <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New "
"Game…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Svi nivoi u igri se snimaju dok igrate, tako da možete pogledati vaše "
"prethodne igre. Također neki nivou imaju zabilježena rješenja, koja vam mogu "
"pomoći da lakše pobjedite. Koristeći <guimenu>Pokret</guimenu> meni i "
"opcije  <guimenuitem>Prikaži sva rješenja </guimenuitem>,<guimenuitem>Pusti "
"isječak ponovo</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Ponovi prethodni nivo</"
"guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Ponovi bilo koji nivo</guimenuitem>. Rješenja "
"i ponavljanje se mogu prekinuti bilo kada klikanjem mišem na igricu, "
"pritiskom na spacebar ili odabirom kratice na meniju (kao što su "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra </guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova Igra ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Instant Replay</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Replay Last "
"Level</guimenuitem> let you continue playing after an interruption. So if "
"things are not going well, you can use <guimenuitem>Instant Replay</"
"guimenuitem>, interrupt the replay at some point and then try another "
"approach. Or if the hero died already, you can use <guimenuitem>Replay Last "
"Level</guimenuitem> in the same way. These features can help you build up a "
"solution to a difficult level in stages, but using them will invalidate any "
"high score you might be working on."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ponovi odmah</guimenuitem> i<guimenuitem>Ponovi prethodni nivo</"
"guimenuitem> omogućava vam da nastavite igrati nakon prekida. dakle, ako "
"loše krene možete iskoristiti<guimenuitem>Ponovi odmah</guimenuitem>, "
"prekinuti ponavljanje i pokušati nešto drugačije. Ako vam heroj imre prije "
"toga, možete iskoristiti <guimenuitem>Ponovi poslednji nivo</guimenuitem> na "
"isti način. Ove opcije vam mogu pomoći kod težih nivoa, ali će vam poništiti "
"rekord."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scoring"
msgstr "Bodovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Start with 5 lives."
msgid "Start with 5 lives"
msgstr "Počni sa 5 života."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lose a life and repeat a level when the hero dies"
msgstr "Izgubi život i ponovi nivo kada izgubite život"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gain a life when you complete a level"
msgstr "Osvoji život kada završite nivo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "75 points for trapping an enemy"
msgstr "75 poena po zarobljenom neprijatelju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "75 points for killing an enemy"
msgstr "75 poena za ubijenog neprijatelja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "250 points for collecting gold"
msgstr "250 poena za skupljeno zlato"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "1500 points for completing a level"
msgstr "1500 poena za završen nivo"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choice of Rules"
msgstr "Izbor Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Most of the rules of &kgoldrunner; are covered in the section <link "
#| "linkend=\"how-to-play\">How to Play</link>, however there are two major "
#| "rule settings that affect the style of play: known as <quote>Traditional</"
#| "quote> and <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote>. It is important to know which "
#| "settings are in force when you are playing a game. &kgoldrunner; "
#| "automatically chooses the correct settings for a game when you play one "
#| "of its levels and the rules for each game are shown in the <link linkend="
#| "\"level-selection-dialog\">Level Selection</link> dialog box."
msgid ""
"Most of the rules of &kgoldrunner; are covered in the section <link linkend="
"\"how-to-play\">How to Play</link>, however there are two major rule "
"settings that affect the style of play: known as <quote>Traditional</quote> "
"and <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote>. It is important to know which settings are "
"in force when you are playing a game. &kgoldrunner; automatically chooses "
"the correct settings for a game when you play one of its levels and the "
"rules for each game are shown in the <link linkend=\"select-game-dialog"
"\">Select Game</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Većina pravila &kgoldrunner;  navedena su u <link linkend=\"how-to-play"
"\">Kako igrati</link>, ipak postoja dvije glavne postavke pravila koja utiču "
"na stil igranja: poznata kao <quote>Standardno</quote> i <quote>&kgoldrunner;"
"</quote>.Važno je znati koja se pravila koriste kada igrate igricu."
"&kgoldrunner; automatski bira ispravne postavke za igru kada igrate neki od "
"nivoa, a pravila za svaku igru su prikazana u <link linkend=\"level-"
"selection-dialog\">Izbor Nivoa</link> dijalogu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main difference between <quote>Traditional</quote> and "
"<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> settings is the method by which the enemies "
"choose a path to the hero."
msgstr ""
"Glavna razlika između <quote>Tradicionalnih</quote> i<quote>&kgoldrunner;</"
"quote>  postavki je način na koji neprijatelji biraju put do heroja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <quote>Traditional</quote> search method, enemies look for vertical "
"paths (ladders and falls) and they try to stay higher than the hero or at "
"the same height. They go below him only as a last resort. The enemies make "
"no attempt to chase the hero in the horizontal direction until they are at "
"the same height and can find a horizontal path. This leads to situations "
"where you can <quote>control</quote> enemies who are far away from you and "
"make them work for you or at least keep out of your hair."
msgstr ""
"Kod <quote>Traditional</quote>  metode traženja, neprijatelji gledaju "
"vertikalne puteve(merdevine ipadove) i pokušavaju biti iznad ili na istoj "
"visini kao heroj. Neprijatelji ne ganjaju heroja horizontalno sve dok nisu "
"na istom nivou. Što pomaže heroju da <quote>kontroliše</quote> neprijatelje "
"ili ih drži na sigurnoj udaljenosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> method searches alternately for horizontal "
"and vertical paths, which tends to keep the enemies over your side of the "
"playing area and at about the same height (&ie; they are more aggressive and "
"not so easy to manipulate). That leads to a more action-packed game, but "
"with less opportunity for strategy and puzzle-solving. However the "
"<quote>State of Terror</quote> game, added in 2007, uses <quote>&kgoldrunner;"
"</quote> rules and has plenty of puzzles to solve while you are on the run. "
"That is why it is such a difficult game."
msgstr ""
"The <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> metoda traženja traži alternativne "
"horizontalne puteve, čime se neprijatelji drže tik do heroja ili odmah iznad "
"njega (&ie; agresivniji su i teško ih je kontrolisati).Ovo dovodi do mnogo "
"dinamicnije igre ali i ostavlja manje prostora za strategiju i mozganje. "
"Ipak u igri <quote>Stanje Terora</quote> dodanoj 2007 koja koristi "
"<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> pravila ali takđer i zahtjeva dosta mozganja."
"Što je čini jako zahtjevnom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "The other differences are listed below:"
msgstr "Još neke razlike su navedene ispod:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> play, the hero and enemies move at fixed "
"speeds in every level and bricks always take the same time to close. In "
"<quote>Traditional</quote> play, the game speed depends on the number of "
"enemies in a level. The more enemies, the slower they run. The hero also "
"becomes slower, but not so noticeably."
msgstr ""
"U <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> igra, brzine heroja i neprijatelja su iste za "
"svaki nivo, te se i zamke zatvaraju istom brzinom. Dok u <quote>Standardno</"
"quote> igri brzina igre zavisi od broja neprijatelje u nivou. Odnosno više "
"neprijatelja, sporija igra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <quote>Traditional</quote> play, enemies always collect gold nuggets when "
"they run into them. In <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> play, it is a random "
"choice. The enemies drop nuggets after a random time in both types of play."
msgstr ""
"U <quote>Tradicionalnoj</quote>igri, neprijatelji uvijek kupe zlato kada "
"naiđu na njeg. Dok je u <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote>  igri slučajno. "
"Neprijatelji ispuštaju zlato poslije nasumično vremena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enemies can run horizontally through holes in <quote>Traditional</quote> "
"play but not in <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> play. The trick in several "
"<quote>Traditional</quote> levels depends on releasing an enemy from behind "
"a brick wall. When you dig away the bricks, he runs out through the hole. In "
"some <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> levels, on the other hand, you must hide "
"inside or behind a dug brick to escape an enemy."
msgstr ""
"Neprijatelji mogu trčati horizontalno kroz rupe u  <quote>Tradicionalnoj</"
"quote> igri ali ne i u <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> igri. Trik u nekoliko "
"<quote>Tradicionalnih</quote> nivoa zavisi od puštanja neprijatelja iza zida."
"Kada prokopate kroz cigle on pobjegne kroz rupu. Dok u nekim "
"<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote>  nivoima morate se sakriti u rupu ili iza zida "
"da pobjegnete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enemies die in <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> play, they go back to where "
"they started the level. In <quote>Traditional</quote> play, they reappear at "
"a random place near the top of the playing area. This makes a big "
"difference, especially in levels where you have to get enemies to fetch "
"nuggets down for you, but also because the enemies keep falling down onto "
"you as fast as you can kill them."
msgstr ""
"Kada naprijatelji umru u <quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> igri, idi na mijesto "
"gdje su bili na početku nivoa. Dok u <quote>Standardno</quote> igri "
"pojavljuju se nasumično blizu vrha. Što čini veliku razliku, jer na nekim "
"nivoima morate natjerati neprijatelje da vam donesu zlato, ali i zbog toga "
"što se pojavljuju iznad vas jednako brzo koliko vam treba da ih ubijete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:569
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The Level Selection Dialog"
msgid "The Select Game Dialog"
msgstr "Izbornik Nivoa"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:572
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Using the Level Selection Dialog Box"
msgid "Using the Select Game Dialog"
msgstr "Koristi Izbornik Nivoa Dijalog"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:574
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>The Level Selection dialog</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>The Select Game dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbornik Nivoa Dijalog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:580
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<phrase>The Level Selection dialog</phrase>"
msgid "<phrase>The Select Game dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbornik Nivoa Dijalog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This box appears when you select the <guimenuitem>New Game</guimenuitem> "
#| "action and also when you select items from the <guimenu>Editor</guimenu> "
#| "menu or replays from the <guimenu>Move</guimenu> menu. You use it to "
#| "choose a game and a level to play, replay, edit, save, move, re-number or "
#| "delete. The main button at the bottom is the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
#| "button. Its label changes according to what you are doing: in this case "
#| "choosing a game and level to play."
msgid ""
"This dialog appears when you select the <guimenuitem>New Game…</guimenuitem> "
"action and also when you select options from the <guimenu>Editor</guimenu> "
"menu or any replay option from the <guimenu>Move</guimenu> menu. You use it "
"to choose a game and a level to play, replay, edit, save, move, re-number or "
"delete. The main button at the bottom is the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button. Its label changes according to what you are doing: in this case "
"choosing a game and level to play."
msgstr ""
"Ova kutija će se prikazati kada odaberete <guimenuitem>Nova Igra</"
"guimenuitem> opciju a i kada odaberete element sa  <guimenu>Izmijeni</"
"guimenu>menija ili Ponovo pusti sa  <guimenu>Pokreni</guimenu> menija. "
"Koristi se da izaberete igru i nivo da igrate,ponovno igrate, izmijenite, "
"spasite,ponovno numerišete ili obrišete. Glavno dugme na dnu je "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>  dugme. Njegova labela se mijenja u zavisnosti šta "
"radite:u ovom slučaju izbor igre i nivoa za igranje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting a Game"
msgstr "Izbor Igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:596
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are several <quote>System</quote> games that come with the "
#| "&kgoldrunner; release and you can add your own games by using the editor. "
#| "All these games appear in the list at the top of the dialog box, grouped "
#| "by level of difficulty. The tutorial games appear last in the list and "
#| "the games of normal skill appear first. To select one of the games, just "
#| "click on its name."
msgid ""
"There are several <quote>System</quote> games that come with the "
"&kgoldrunner; release and you can add your own games by using the editor. "
"All these games appear in the list at the top of the dialog, grouped by "
"level of difficulty. The tutorial games appear last in the list and the "
"games of normal skill appear first. To select one of the games, just click "
"on its name."
msgstr ""
"Postoji nekoliko <quote>Sistem</quote>igara koje dolaze sa &kgoldrunner; "
"paketom ali i vi možete dodati svoje koristeći editor. Sve ove igre "
"smještene su na vrhu liste dijalog kutije i grupisane su po težini nivoa. "
"Tutorijalske igrice su zadnje na listi dok su normalne pri vrhu. Za izbor "
"jednostavno kliknite na ime igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list shows what rule settings apply to each game (see <link linkend="
"\"choice-of-rules\">Choice of Rules</link>) and how many levels there are. "
"When you select a game, a box lower down the screen shows you further "
"information about that game."
msgstr ""
"Lista prikazuje pravila koja važe za svaku igru(vidi<link linkend=\"choice-"
"of-rules\">Izbor Pravila</link>) i koliko ima nivoa. Kada odaberete igru, "
"kutija u dnu ekrana prikazat će vam dodatne informacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting a Level"
msgstr "Izbor Nivoa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to start a game at any level, but it is best to start at "
"level 1 and work up, especially if you are going for a high score. In "
"general, the higher numbered levels are more difficult."
msgstr ""
"Možete započeti igru na bilo kojem nivou, ali je ipak najbolje početi od "
"nivoa 1 pa ići dalje, posebno ako želite postići rekord. Općenito su viši "
"nivoi i teži."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you start the level selection dialog, the default level will be "
#| "something reasonable, such as the last level you played or edited. You "
#| "can select another level by using the spinbox arrows, by typing the level "
#| "number into the spinbox or by moving the slider. The arrows at the ends "
#| "of the slider increase or decrease the number by one. Also you can drag "
#| "the slider with the left mouse button held down and change the level "
#| "number rapidly. Or you can change the level number in steps of 10 by "
#| "clicking in the space above or below the slider handle."
msgid ""
"When you start the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog, the default "
"level will be something reasonable, such as the last level you played or "
"edited. You can select another level by using the spinbox arrows, by typing "
"the level number into the spinbox or by moving the slider. The arrows at the "
"ends of the slider increase or decrease the number by one. Also you can drag "
"the slider with the &LMB; held down and change the level number rapidly. Or "
"you can change the level number in steps of 10 by clicking in the space "
"above or below the slider handle."
msgstr ""
"Kada uđete u izbornik nivoa dijalog, unaprijed određeni nivo će biti razumno "
"odabran, na primjer zadnji nivo koji ste igrali ili izmijenili. Možete "
"izabrati drugi nivo koristeći spinbox strelice, ukucavajući broj nivoa u "
"spinbox ili pomijerajući klizač. Strelice na kraju klizača povećavaju ili "
"smanjuju vrijednost za 1. Također možete brzo promijeniti vrijednost nivoa "
"lijevim klikom miša. Ili možete pritiskom na spacebar mijenjati vrijednost "
"po 10 iznad i ispod klizača."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As the level number changes, a preview of the level appears in the small "
"preview window and the level's name (if it has one) also appears."
msgstr ""
"Kada se promijeni nivo, prikazat će se u malom ekranu ime nivoa(ako ga ima) "
"ali i njegov prikaz."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completing your Selection"
msgstr "Popunjavanje vašeg Izbora"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have chosen a game and level, just click the main button at the "
"bottom and proceed with your edit, play or replay."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste izabrali igru i nivo, kliknite na glavno dugme u dnu i nastavite sa "
"izmjenama, igrom ili ponavljenjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:637
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Until you do that, nothing changes, so you can always click "
#| "<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> and go back to what you were doing earlier. "
#| "Note that the game action is frozen while the dialog box is active, so "
#| "you can continue playing where you left off if you choose "
#| "<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton>."
msgid ""
"Until you do that, nothing changes, so you can always click "
"<guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> and go back to what you were doing earlier. "
"Note that the game action is frozen while the dialog is active, so you can "
"continue playing where you left off if you choose <guibutton>Cancel</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Sve dok to ne uradite ništa se ne mijenja, ali uvijek možete kliknuti click "
"<guibutton>Odustani</guibutton> i vratiti se na šta ste radili ranije. "
"Zapamtite da igra miruje sve dok je dijalog kutija aktivna, tako da možete "
"nastaviti igrati ako odabrete <guibutton>Odustani</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Changes"
msgstr "Spasi Izmjene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:648
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you select an action on the <guimenu>Game</guimenu>, <guimenu>Editor</"
#| "guimenu> or <guimenu>Move</guimenu> menu and you were previously editing "
#| "and had not saved your changes, you will get a message asking you to "
#| "save, abandon or continue your work. Neither the new action nor its "
#| "dialog will begin until you have made a decision about your previous work."
msgid ""
"If you select an option on the <guimenu>Game</guimenu>, <guimenu>Editor</"
"guimenu> or <guimenu>Move</guimenu> menus and you were previously editing "
"and had not saved your changes, you will get a message asking you to save, "
"abandon or continue your work. Neither the new action nor its dialog will "
"begin until you have made a decision about your previous work."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste izabrali opciju na <guimenu>Igra</guimenu>, <guimenu>Izmjene</"
"guimenu> or <guimenu>Pokreni</guimenu> meniju a prije toga ste mijenjali "
"sadržaj a nista spasili svoje izmjene, dobit ćete poruku koja vas pita da li "
"želite spasiti, napustiti ili nastaviti vaš rad. Niti nova akcija niti "
"dijalog mogu poćeti dok ne donesete svoju odluku vezanu za prethodni rad."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing or Editing <quote>Any</quote> Level"
msgstr "Igranje ili Izmjene  <quote>Bilo koji</quote>Nivo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the menus and dialog allow you to select and play or edit "
"<quote>any</quote> level. If you start a game after level 1, that is OK, you "
"will just not get such a high score. Dedicated players often prefer to play "
"high-numbered levels for fun, rather than go for a high score, or they might "
"like to <quote>train</quote> on higher levels before attempting a high score."
msgstr ""
"Primijetite da meniji i dijalozi vam dopuštaju da igrate ili mijenjate "
"<quote>bilo koji</quote>nivo. Ako počnete igru poslije nivoa 1, to je OK,"
"samo što vam rekor neće biti velik. Posvećeni igrači četo biraju više nivoe "
"za zabavu,a ne za rekord ili jednostavno <quote>uvježbavaju</quote> vještinu "
"na višim nivoima prije nego krenu po rekord."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a System level for editing, that is OK too, but you must save "
"it in one of your own games: not back in the System game. For example you "
"might want to modify a very difficult level so that you do not go back to "
"the start of the level every time you die."
msgstr ""
"Ako izaberete Sistem nivo za izmjene, to je isto OK, ali ga morate spasiti u "
"svoju igricu: a ne u Sistem igricu. Na primjer, želite izmijeniti neki jako "
"težak nivo ali ne želite se vraćati na početak nivoa svaki put kada umrete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see what this means, try the <quote>Challenge</quote> game, level 16, "
"<quote>The Three Musketeers</quote>. That level has about ten difficult "
"puzzles in it. When you have solved puzzle 1, you do not want to keep "
"repeating it while you work on puzzle 2. The secret is to make an editable "
"copy, then keep updating it and changing the hero's starting point, until "
"you have solved all the puzzles. Then you can go back and attempt the real "
"thing, from start to finish."
msgstr ""
"Da biste bolje vidjeli sta ovo znači, pokušajte sa  <quote>Izazov</quote> "
"igrom, nivo 16 <quote>Tri Mušketira</quote>. Taj nivo ima 10 različitih "
"mozgalica. Kada rješite jednu, ne želite je ponavljati svaki put dok "
"rješavate drugu. Tajna je u tome da napravite izmjenjivu kopiju, a onda je "
"učitavata i mijenjate početno mijesto heroja sve dok ne rješite sve "
"mozgalice. Onda se možete vratiti i pokušati preći stvarni nivo od početka "
"do kraja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menu Reference"
msgstr "Referenca na Meni"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview of Menus"
msgstr "Pregled Menija"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game"
msgstr "Igra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:694
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This menu contains options affecting game play, such as starting and "
#| "finishing games, saving games, loading saved games and showing high "
#| "scores (if available). The <guimenu>Game</guimenu> Menu also contains the "
#| "<guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> option, or you can quit by clicking the "
#| "<guiicon>X</guiicon> at the top right of the &kgoldrunner; window."
msgid ""
"This menu contains options affecting game play, such as starting and "
"finishing games, saving games, loading saved games and showing high scores "
"(if available). Also contains the <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> option, or "
"you can quit by clicking the <guiicon>X</guiicon> at the top right of the "
"&kgoldrunner; window."
msgstr ""
"Meni sadrži opcije koje utiču na igranje, kao što su početak i kraj igre, "
"snimanje igara, pokretanje snimljenih igara i prikaz rekorda(ako ih ima). "
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> Meni također sadrži opciju <guimenuitem>Prekid</"
"guimenuitem> ili možete prekinuti klikom na  <guiicon>X</guiicon>u gornjem "
"desnom uglu &kgoldrunner; prozora."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move"
msgstr "Kreni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains an option to get a hint (if there is one). Championship "
"and Tutorial games have hints on every level. Other games rarely have hints. "
"It also contains options to replay recordings of play, as when running "
"demonstrations, showing examples of solutions and replaying your own efforts."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj meni sadrži opciju za pomoć(ako postoji). Šampionske i Tutorijalske "
"igre imaju pomoć na svakom nivou.Druge igre rijetko imaju pomoć. Također "
"sadrži opciju da se pregledaju snimci igranja, kao što je prikaz "
"demonstracije, prikaz primjera i ponovni prikaz vaših pokušaja."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:716
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu contains an option to alternate the full screen mode."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor"
msgstr "Urednik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu has everything you need to create your own games and levels and "
"maintain them, including features to help you re-order levels or move them "
"between games or to delete them when no longer needed. When you reorganize "
"your levels, the level numbers in your game remain consecutive (no gaps) and "
"the levels are automatically renumbered."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj meni ima sve potrebno da kreirate svoju igru i nivoe i da ih spasite, "
"uključujući dodatne opcije kojima možete reorganizovati nivoe ili ih "
"razmijeniti između igara ili ih obrisati ako vam više ne trebaju. Kada "
"reorganizujete vaše nivoe, broj nivoa će biti dosljedan(bez preskoka) jer će "
"se oni automatski numerisati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are using the Game Editor a graphical toolbar with tool tip text "
"appears under the menu bar. See the <link linkend=\"game-editor\">Game "
"Editor</link> for more details of how to create and edit &kgoldrunner; "
"levels."
msgstr ""
"Kada koristite Urednik Igre grafička traka alata sa kratkim opisima alata će "
"se prikazati u meni traki. Vidi <link linkend=\"game-editor\">Urednik Igre</"
"link>  za više detalja kako kreirati i izmijeniti &kgoldrunner; nivoe."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu has several groups of &kgoldrunner; settings, including the choice "
"of mouse, keyboard or hybrid (laptop) control and the choices of themes and "
"game-speed. The current selections are checked. The settings are "
"automatically selected when you start playing, but you can use this menu to "
"vary them if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj meni ima nekoliko grupa  &kgoldrunner;  postavki, uključujući i izbor "
"miša,tastature ili hibrida(laptop) za kontrolu heroja i za izbor tema i "
"brzine igre. Trenute selekcije su označene. Ova postavka je automatski "
"označena kad počnete igrati, ali možete koristiti ovaj meni da ih "
"promijenite po želji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also an option to re-assign keyboard shortcuts and hero-control "
"keys."
msgstr ""
"Također postoji i opcija da reorganizuje kratice tastature i tipke kontrole "
"heroja."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoć"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:754
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu contains access to the &kgoldrunner; "
#| "Handbook (this document), <guimenuitem>About &kgoldrunner;</guimenuitem> "
#| "and <guimenuitem>About &kde;</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu contains access to the &kgoldrunner; "
"Handbook (this document), <guimenuitem>About &kgoldrunner;</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>About &kde;</guimenuitem> options."
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoć</guimenu> meni zadrži pristup  &kgoldrunner; Priručniku(ovaj "
"dokument),<guimenuitem>O &kgoldrunner;</guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>O &kde;</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid "There is also an option to report a Bug or Wishlist item."
msgstr "Postoji i opcija koja prijavljuje Bug ili element iz Liste želja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:758
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you would like to make a suggestion or you have some new levels to "
#| "contribute, the current author's email address is in the "
#| "<guimenuitem>About &kgoldrunner;</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgid ""
"If you would like to make a suggestion or you have some new levels to "
"contribute, the current author's email address is in the <guimenuitem>About "
"&kgoldrunner;</guimenuitem> option."
msgstr ""
"Ako imate neke primjedbe ili prijedloge ili imate neke svoje nivoe, email "
"adresa autora je u<guimenuitem>O &kgoldrunner; </guimenuitem> meni element."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "Meni Igre"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:772
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
#| "shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Game...</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Game…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova Igra...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Shows the level selection dialog box (see <link linkend=\"level-selection-"
#| "dialog-box\"> Using the Level Selection Dialog Box</link>), where you "
#| "choose a game and a level within that game. At first it is easiest to "
#| "start at level 1, because the levels are arranged approximately in order "
#| "of difficulty. Also it is best to start there if you are going for a high "
#| "score."
msgid ""
"Shows the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog (see <link linkend="
"\"select-game-dialog-box\"> Using the Select Game Dialog</link>), where you "
"choose a game and a level within that game. At first it is easiest to start "
"at level 1, because the levels are arranged approximately in order of "
"difficulty. Also it is best to start there if you are going for a high score."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje Izbor nivoa dijalog kutiju (vidi <link linkend=\"level-selection-"
"dialog-box\"> Koristi Izbor Nivoa Dijalog Kutiju</link>),gdje možete "
"odabrati igru i nivo unutar nje. Ispočetka bolje je krenuti od nivoa 1, jer "
"su nivoi poredani po težini.Također ako krenete od nivoa 1 bolje su vam "
"šanse za rekord."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:788
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
#| "shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Load Saved Game...</"
#| "guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Load Saved Game…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokreni Spašenu Igru...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Brings up a table of previously saved games, sorted with the latest first. "
"Each line lists the game, level, number of lives, score, day of week, date "
"and time. If you select a line and click the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button, that game starts at the beginning of that level, with the lives and "
"score you saved."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje tabeli prethodno spašenih igara, retrospektivno.U svakoj liniji je "
"navedena igra,nivo, broj života,rekord,dan u sedmici, datum i vrijeme. Ako "
"odaberete liniju i kliknete <guibutton>OK</guibutton>  dugme, igra počinje "
"sa tog nivoa sa životima i rekordom koji ste spasili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>Y</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Play Next Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>Y</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Igraj Sledeći Nivo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Loads the next level in the current game, ready to play and without any "
"further dialog. You can use this to browse quickly through the levels of a "
"game."
msgstr ""
"Učitava sledeći nivo u ovoj igri, spremno za igru bez dijaloga ubuduće. Ovo "
"možete koristiti da brzo prezražite nivoe u igri."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:815
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut><keycap>S</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Game...</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>S</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Game…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>S</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Spasi Igru...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:820
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Saves the current game, level, lives and score. The option will only save "
#| "the position and score as at the start of the current level. You can save "
#| "when you are mid-way through a level, but &kgoldrunner; will still save "
#| "the position (and score) as it was at the start of the level. You will "
#| "receive a warning message about that. Before using this option, you "
#| "should press a Pause key (<keycap>P</keycap> or &Esc;), to freeze the "
#| "game as you move the mouse, but it is much easier to use the <keycap>S</"
#| "keycap> key as a short-cut."
msgid ""
"Saves the current game, level, lives and score. The option will only save "
"the position and score as at the start of the current level. You can save "
"when you are mid-way through a level, but &kgoldrunner; will still save the "
"position (and score) as it was at the start of the level. You will receive a "
"warning message about that. Before using this option, you should press a "
"Pause key (<keycap>P</keycap> or &Esc;), to freeze the game as you move the "
"mouse, but it is much easier to use the <keycap>S</keycap> key as a shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Spašava trenutnu igru,nivo,živote i rekord. Ova opcija će spasiti poziciju i "
"rekord na početku nivoa. Možete spasiti kada ste na pola nivoa ali  "
"&kgoldrunner; će ipak spasiti poziciju i rekord na početku nivoa. Primit "
"ćete upozorenje koje vam govori to. Prije korištenja ove opcije, trebali bi "
"ste pritisnuti Pauzu(<keycap>P</keycap> ili &Esc;),da zaustavi igru kada "
"pomijerate miš, ali je laše ako koristite  <keycap>S</keycap>  tipku kao "
"kraticu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:833
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
#| "keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Edits...</"
#| "guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Edits…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spasi Izmjene...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:838
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This option is enabled only if you have been using the Game Editor. It "
#| "brings up the level selection dialog box and lets you choose a level "
#| "number and game in which to save your work. Its action is exactly the "
#| "same as the <guimenuitem>Save Edits</guimenuitem> option on the "
#| "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu> menu and the <guiicon>disk</guiicon> icon on "
#| "the Editor toolbar."
msgid ""
"This option is enabled only if you have been using the Game Editor. It "
"brings up the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog and lets you choose a "
"level number and game in which to save your work. Its action is exactly the "
"same as the <menuchoice><guimenu>Editor</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Edits…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item and the <guiicon>disk</guiicon> icon on "
"the Editor toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija je moguća samo kad koristite Urednik Igre. Prikazuje Izbornik "
"nivoa dijalog kutiju i daje vam mogućnost izbora broja nivoa i igre gdje "
"ćete spasiti vaše izmjene. Ovo akcija je identična opciji <guimenuitem>Spasi "
"Izmjene</guimenuitem> na  <guimenu>Urednik</guimenu> meniju i <guiicon>disk</"
"guiicon> ikoni na Urednik taki alata."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:848
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
#| "keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Edits...</"
#| "guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save a Solution…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spasi Izmjene...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save a solution for a level into a file called "
"<quote><filename>sol_<replaceable>prefix</replaceable>.txt</filename></"
"quote> in your user's data directory."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P or &Esc;</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P or &Esc;</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pauza</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stops or restarts the game action."
msgstr "Zaustavlja ili restartuje igricu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:871
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></"
#| "keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show High "
#| "Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show High Scores…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži Rekorde</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a table of up to ten high scores for the currently selected game. Each "
"line shows the player's rank and name, the level reached, the score "
"achieved, the day of the week and the date."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje tabelu od deset najboljih rekorda za izabranu igricu. Svaki red "
"prikazije ime igrača i poziciju , nivo do kojeg je došao, njegov rekord, dan "
"u sedmici i datum."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>Q</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kill Hero</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>Q</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Samoubistvo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kills the hero when he is in a position from which he cannot escape."
msgstr "Počinite samoubistvo kada ste u poziciji iz koje se ne možete izvući."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prekini</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Terminates &kgoldrunner; immediately. If a game is in progress, it "
"disappears forever (unless you have just saved it) and there is no check for "
"a high score. If you were editing a level, you are given an opportunity to "
"save your work."
msgstr ""
"Prekida  &kgoldrunner; odmah. Ako je igra pokrenuta, nestaje "
"zauvijek(ukoliko je nista spasili) i ne pamti rekord. Ako ste mijenjali "
"nivo, daće vam šansu da spasite rad."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Move Menu"
msgstr "Pokretni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:915
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "All the demo and replay moves will replay previously recorded levels. All "
#| "can be interrupted and stopped by clicking on the playing area with the "
#| "mouse, pressing the spacebar or selecting a menu item or shortcut (such "
#| "as <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Game...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgid ""
"All the demo and replay moves will replay previously recorded levels. All "
"can be interrupted and stopped by clicking on the playing area with the "
"mouse, pressing the &Space; bar or selecting a menu item or shortcut (such "
"as <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Game…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Svi demo snimku i potezi će reproducirati prethodno snimljeni nivoa. Sve se "
"može prekinuti i zaustavio klikom na igru s mišem , pritiskom na razmaknicu "
"ili odabirom stavke izbornika ili prečica ( kao što "
"su<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova igra...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pokreni</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Naputak</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a popup hint, if there is one for the level being played. By "
"convention, Championship and Tutorial games have hints on every level. Other "
"games rarely have hints. The lower part of the &kgoldrunner; window shows "
"whether a hint is available or not."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje naputak, ako postoji za nivo koji igrate. Po konvenciji, Šampionat "
"i Tutorijal igre imaju naputke na svim nivoima. Druge igre rijetko imaju "
"naputke. Donji dio &kgoldrunner;  prozora će pokazati da li je naputak "
"dostupan ili ne."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pokreni</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plays a demonstration of play in a few recorded levels. These are the same "
"as in the startup demo."
msgstr ""
"Pušta demonstraciju igre na nekoliko snimljenih nivoa.Istih kao i pri "
"pokretanju igre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:948
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show A Solution...</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show a Solution</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pokreni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži Rješenje...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replays a recorded solution of a level, if there is a solution on file in "
"the released game-data."
msgstr ""
"Pušta spašeno rješenje nivoa, ako takvo postoji u datoteci informacija igre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Instant Replay</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pokreni</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Odmah Pusti Ponovljeni Snimak</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stops play in the current level and replays the recorded version from the "
"beginning. If you interrupt the replay, you can continue playing from that "
"point and try another approach. You can use this feature to build up a "
"winning sequence of moves in stages, but that will invalidate any high score "
"you might be working on."
msgstr ""
"Zaustavlja igru na trenutnom nivou i ponavlja zabilježenu verziju od "
"početka. Ako prekinete ponavljanje, možete nastaviti igrati sa mijesta gdje "
"ste stali ili probati drugi pristup. Ovo vam može pomoći da redate pobijede,"
"ali će vam poništiti rekord."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Replay Last Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pokreni</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovi Prethodni Nivo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replays the recorded version of the last level you played, from the "
"beginning (&eg; if you lost the level). If you interrupt the replay, you can "
"continue playing from that point and try another approach. You can use this "
"feature to build up a winning sequence of moves in stages, but that will "
"invalidate any high score you might be working on."
msgstr ""
"Ponavlja zadnju zabilježenu verziju nivoa kojeg ste igrali, od početka(&eg; "
"npr. ako ste izgubili). Ako prekinete ponavljanje ko prekinete ponavljanje, "
"možete nastaviti igrati sa mijesta gdje ste stali ili probati drugi pristup. "
"Ovo vam može pomoći da redate pobijede,ali će vam poništiti rekord."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Replay Any Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pokreni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovi Bilo Koji Nivo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replays the recorded version of any level you have previously played."
msgstr ""
"Ponavlja zabilježenu verziju bilo kojeg nivoa kojeg ste prethodno igrali."

