#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor Menu"
msgstr "Urednički Meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Level</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Urednik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kreiraj Nivo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1032
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Shows the Editor toolbar and a blank playing area on which you can draw a "
#| "new level. When done, use <guimenuitem>Save Edits</guimenuitem> to assign "
#| "the new level to a game and level number."
msgid ""
"Shows the Editor toolbar and a blank playing area on which you can draw a "
"new level. When done, use the <guimenuitem>Save Edits…</guimenuitem> option "
"to assign the new level to a game and level number."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje Uredničku traku alata i prazn nivo koji možete urediti. Kada "
"završite, koristite <guimenuitem>Spasi Izmjene</guimenuitem> da dodate nivo "
"igri i broj nivou."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1040
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Level...</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Level…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Urednik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uredi Nivo...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1045
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Shows the level selection dialog box, where you choose a game and level "
#| "to edit. You can choose a System game and level, but you get a warning "
#| "that you can only save the edited level in one of your own games."
msgid ""
"Shows the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog, where you choose a game "
"and level to edit. You can choose a System game and level, but you get a "
"warning that you can only save the edited level in one of your own games."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži izbor nivoa dijalog kutiju, u kojoj možete odabrati igru i nivo koji "
"želite izmijeniti. Možete izabrati Sistemsku igu i nivo, ali će vas "
"upozoriti da izmijenjen nivo možete spasiti samo u svoju igru."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1053
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></"
#| "keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Edits...</"
#| "guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Edits…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Urednik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spasi Izmijene...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1059
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Shows the level selection dialog box with appropriate default settings "
#| "for saving a new or edited level. You can change the game and level "
#| "number and achieve a <quote>Save As...</quote> effect. This dialog box "
#| "has a special button, <guibutton>Edit Level Name and Hint</guibutton>, "
#| "which shows a dialog box where you can add an optional name and hint to "
#| "your level."
msgid ""
"Shows the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog with appropriate default "
"settings for saving a new or edited level. You can change the game and level "
"number and achieve a <quote>Save As…</quote> effect. This dialog has a "
"special button, <guibutton>Edit Level Name or Hint</guibutton>, which shows "
"a dialog where you can add an optional name and hint to your level."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje izbor nivoa dijelog kutiju sa a unaprijed određenim postavkama za "
"snimanje novog ili izmijenjenog nivoa. Možete snimiti igru i broj nivoa te "
"postići isti efekat kao sa <quote>Spasi Kao...</quote>. Dijalog kutija ima "
"posebno dugme,<guibutton>Uredi Ime Nivoa i Naputak</guibutton>,koje "
"prikazuje dijalog kutiju u kojij možete navesti izabrano ime i naputak za "
"taj nivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1069
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Move Level...</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Move Level…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Urednik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premjesti Nivo...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1074
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This is a two-part operation. Before using <guimenuitem>Move Level</"
#| "guimenuitem>, you must load a level to be moved by selecting it for play "
#| "or edit. The <guimenuitem>Move Level</guimenuitem> option then shows the "
#| "level selection dialog box, where you choose a new place for the loaded "
#| "level. You can change both the game and the level number, to move a level "
#| "to another game, or you can just change the level number to re-order "
#| "levels within a game. You cannot move a System level."
msgid ""
"This is a two-part operation. Before using <guimenuitem>Move Level…</"
"guimenuitem>, you must load a level to be moved by selecting it for play or "
"edit. Then shows the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog, where you "
"choose a new place for the loaded level. You can change both the game and "
"the level number, to move a level to another game, or you can just change "
"the level number to re-order levels within a game. You cannot move a System "
"level."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je operacija u dva koraka. Prije korištenja <guimenuitem>Premjesti Nivo</"
"guimenuitem>, morate pokrenuti nivo koji želite premjestiti, tako što ćete "
"ga označiti za igru ili izmjene.  <guimenuitem>Premjesti Nivo</"
"guimenuitem>ocija prikazuje izbornik nivoa dijalog kutiju, kada izabrete "
"mijesto gdje ćete staviti pokrenuti nivo. Možete izmijeniti i igru i broj "
"nivoa,  premijestite nivo u drugu igru, ili samo preorganizovati brojeve "
"nivoa. Sistemski nivo se ne može premještati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1086
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete Level...</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete Level…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Urednik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Obriši nivo...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Shows the level selection dialog box, where you choose a level to delete. "
#| "You cannot delete a System level."
msgid ""
"Shows the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog, where you choose a level "
"to delete. You cannot delete a System level."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje izbornik nivoa dijalog kutiju, gdje možete izabrati nivo koji "
"želite obrisati. Sistemski nivo se ne mogu brisati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1097
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Game...</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Game…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Urednik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kreiraj Igru...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You need to use this option before you start creating your own "
#| "&kgoldrunner; levels. It shows a dialog box where you can enter the name "
#| "of a new game, a 1-5 character prefix for level-file names, the default "
#| "rules for your game (<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> or <quote>Traditional</"
#| "quote>) and an optional description or comment about the game."
msgid ""
"You need to use this option before you start creating your own &kgoldrunner; "
"levels. It shows a dialog where you can enter the name of a new game, a 1-5 "
"character prefix for level-file names, the default rules for your game "
"(<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> or <quote>Traditional</quote>) and an optional "
"description or comment about the game."
msgstr ""
"Ovo upciju treba koristiti prije nego započnete kreiranje vlastitih "
"&kgoldrunner; nivoa. Opcija prikazuje dijalog kutiju gdje možete unijeti ime "
"nove igrice, preiks od 1 do 5 za imena nivoa, i predodređena pravila vaše "
"igre (<quote>&kgoldrunner;</quote> or <quote>Standardno</quote>)i neobavezni "
"opis ili komentar igre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Game Info...</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Editor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Game Info…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uradnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izmijeni Informacije O Igri...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1117
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Shows the level selection dialog box, where you choose a game to be "
#| "edited, then shows the game information in a dialog box where you can "
#| "edit the name, rules and description, but not the file name prefix, in "
#| "case you have saved some levels. That is because the prefix is used in "
#| "level-file names internally."
msgid ""
"Shows the <guilabel>Select Game</guilabel> dialog, where you choose a game "
"to be edited, then shows the game information in a dialog where you can edit "
"the name, rules and description, but not the file name prefix, in case you "
"have saved some levels. That is because the prefix is used in level-file "
"names internally."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje izbornik nivoa dijalog kutiju, kada izaberete igru koju želite "
"izmijeniti, a nakon toga prikazuje informacije u dijalog kutiji u kojij "
"možete izmijeniti ime,pravila,ali ne i prefiks datoteke,ako ste već spasili "
"neke nivoe. Jer se prefiks koristi interno u datoteci imena nivoa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1130
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni Postavki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Change Theme</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guisubmenu>Promijeni Temu</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu offers you a choice of background themes or <quote>worlds</"
"quote> in which to play. You can change the theme at any time, even as the "
"game is playing. For those who are artistically inclined, it is possible to "
"compose new themes, including graphics or sound or both and add them to "
"&kgoldrunner;. Just contact the author for details."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj podmeni nudi mogućnost izbora pozadine teme ili <quote>svjetova</quote> "
"za igru. Temu možete promijeniti bilo kada.Oni koji imaju više umjetničkog "
"dara mogu kreirati nove teme, grafiku iki zvuk i dodati ih u &kgoldrunner;. "
"Kontaktirajte autora za detalje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Treasure of Egypt"
msgstr "Blago Egipta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matt Goldrunner finds himself in an Ancient Egyptian temple, being pursued "
"by mummies who are determined to protect their ancestral jewels at all costs."
msgstr ""
"Matt Goldrunner nalazi se u Dravnom Hramu u Egiptu, progonjen mumijama "
"odlučnim da zaštite nakit svojih predaka po svaku cijenu."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Black on White"
msgstr "Crno na Bijelom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This theme is stripped down to its barest graphical units and painted in "
"black and white only. It is intended to help players who may be visually "
"impaired. The author would appreciate email responses on how effective it is "
"and what improvements in visibility could be made."
msgstr ""
"Ova teme sadrži samo osnovne grafičke detalje a obojena je samo crnom i "
"bijelom bojom. Namijenjena je osobama koje imaju probleme sa vidom.Autor bi "
"bio zahvalan kada bi mu poslali vaše imšljenje i prijedloge emailom."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kgoldrunner; Default"
msgstr "&kgoldrunner; Predodređeno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gives you the default &kgoldrunner; theme, with red bricks and gray concrete."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja predodređenu  &kgoldrunner; temu, sa crvenim ciglama i sivim "
"betonom."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Geek City"
msgstr "Grad Štrebera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Our hero is trapped inside a computer. Will he escape when he finally "
"reaches the last level?"
msgstr ""
"Naš heroj je zarobljen u računaru. Da li će nakon poslednjeg nivoa i "
"pobjeći ?"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nostalgia Blues"
msgstr "Nostalgija Bluz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recalls the Apple II game, where the bricks and concrete were a nice blue "
"color, the hero was white, the enemies had white pants and orange (flesh-"
"tint) tops and the gold was white boxes with orange panels. The whole effect "
"was fuzzier (a sort of hardware anti-aliasing), which made the bricks look "
"almost three-dimensional &mdash; difficult to recreate on today's pin-sharp "
"monitors."
msgstr ""
"Podsjeća na Apple II igricu, u kojoj su cigle i beton bili divne plave boje, "
"a heroj bijele,neprijatelju su nosili bijele pantalone i narandžaste majice, "
"a zlato je bilo u bijelim kutijama sa narandžastim panelima. Efekat je bio "
"zbunjujući(tip hardverskog anti-alijasinga), zbog čega su cigle izgledale "
"gotovo kao da su 3D &mdash; što je teško ponoviti na današnjim monitorima."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nostalgia"
msgstr "Nostalgija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recalls the days of the original Apple II and Commodore 64 game, as it was "
"when you plugged your machine into your TV set &mdash; otherwise you had a "
"monochrome monitor. For those who do not remember such heroic days, this is "
"not an exact reproduction, but it gives you a general idea. For example the "
"hero was all white back then, but today he is blue."
msgstr ""
"Podsjeća se originalnih Apple II i Commodore 64 igrica, koje su se kopčale "
"na vaš TV set &mdash;, jer bi u protivnom imali monohromatski monitor. Za "
"one koji se ne sjećaju ovih historijskih dana, tačna preprodukcija ne "
"postoji,ali možete dobiti kakav takav uvid u stvari. Kao npr. naš heroj je "
"tad bio čisto bijel dok je sada njegova boja plava."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reproduciraj Zvuk</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles the sounds on and off."
msgstr "Pokreće i prekida reprodukciju zvuka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Play Footstep Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reproduciraj Zvuk Koraka</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles the sounds of footsteps on and off."
msgstr "Pokreće i prekida reprodukciju zvuka koraka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo At Start</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Demo Pri Pokretanju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the startup demo on and off (see <link linkend=\"how-to-play"
"\">Starting the Game</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Pokreće i prekida Demo snimak pri pokretanu (vidi<link linkend=\"how-to-play"
"\">Započinjanje Igre</link>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mouse Controls Hero</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kontrole Mišom</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets mouse control of the hero (see <link linkend=\"mouse-control\">Moving "
"Around</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Postavlje kontrole mišom (vidi<link linkend=\"mouse-control\">Kretanje</"
"link>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Controls Hero</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postacke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kontrole Tastaturom</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets keyboard control of the hero (see <link linkend=\"keyboard-control"
"\">Keyboard Control</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja kontrole tastaturom (vidi <link linkend=\"keyboard-control"
"\">Kontrole Tastaturom</link>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Hybrid Control (Laptop)</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Hibridne Kontrole (Laptop)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets hybrid control of the hero, for laptops, where the touchpad or other "
"pointer device is used to guide the hero and the dig keys, on the keyboard, "
"are used for digging left and right."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja hibridne kontrole,za laptope, kada se tačped koristi za navigaciju "
"a tastatura za kopanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Click Key To Move</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pritisni Tipku Za Pokret</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In keyboard mode, click a direction-key to start moving and keep on going "
"until you click another key."
msgstr ""
"Ako koristite tastaturu, pritisnite strelicu da se počnete kretati sve dok "
"ne pritisnete neku drugu tipku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Hold Key To Move</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Drži Tipku Za Kretanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In keyboard mode, hold down a direction-key to move and release it to stop."
